U sĩɑwɑ dee dee Yinni Gusunɔn wuswɑɑɔ. Win tundo Osiɑsin yirɑ u swĩi mɑm mɑm. Adɑmɑ u ǹ due Yinni Gusunɔn sɑ̃ɑ yerɔ. Yen biru, u derɑ tɔmbɑ sɑnkirɑmɔ win tem mɛ sɔɔ.
U Dɑmɑsin bũnu yɑ̃kuru kuɑ ni nu nùn kɑmiɑ mi. Domi u nɛɛ, wee Sirin sinɑ bokon bũnu nu rɑ bu somi. Tɛ̃, win tii u koo mɑɑ nu yɑ̃kuru kuɑ kpɑ nu wɑ nu nùn somi. Adɑmɑ nu ǹ nùn somi. Nu nùn kɑm kuɑwɑ wi kɑ Isirelibɑ kpuro.
Mɑ Lefibɑ bɑ nɑ bɑ sinɑ Yinni Gusunɔn sɑ̃ɑ yerɔ kɑ dwee yɑ̃ɑ ni Dɑfidi u derɑ bɑ kuɑ. Mɑ yɑ̃ku kowobu bɑ mɑɑ duɑ kɑ ben kɔbi.
